 39 |       cargo="cargo tauri add autostart"
 40 |     />
 41 | 
 42 |   </TabItem>
 43 |     <TabItem label="Manual">
 44 |       <Steps>
 45 | 
 46 |         1. Run the following command in the `src-tauri` folder to add the plugin to the project's dependencies in `Cargo.toml`:
 47 | 
 48 |             ```sh frame=none
 49 |             cargo add tauri-plugin-autostart --target 'cfg(any(target_os = "macos", windows, target_os = "linux"))'
 50 |             ```
 51 | 
 52 |         2.  Modify `lib.rs` to initialize the plugin:
 53 | 
