 20 | Allows your mobile application to use the camera to scan QR codes, EAN-13 and other kinds of barcodes.
 21 | 
 22 | ## Supported Platforms
 23 | 
 24 | <Compatibility plugin={frontmatter.plugin} />
 25 | 
 26 | ## Setup
 27 | 
 28 | Install the barcode-scanner plugin to get started.
 29 | 
 30 | <Tabs>
 31 |   <TabItem label="Automatic">
 32 | 
 33 |     Use your project's package manager to add the dependency:
 34 | 
 35 |     {' '}
 36 | 
 37 |     <CommandTabs
