 19 | 
 20 | Prompt the user for biometric authentication on Android and iOS.
 21 | 
 22 | ## Supported Platforms
 23 | 
 24 | <Compatibility plugin={frontmatter.plugin} />
 25 | 
 26 | ## Setup
 27 | 
 28 | Install the biometric plugin to get started.
 29 | 
 30 | <Tabs>
 31 |     <TabItem label="Automatic">
 32 | 
 33 |     Use your project's package manager to add the dependency:
 34 | 
 35 |     <CommandTabs npm="npm run tauri add biometric"
