 44 |         <Steps>
 45 |         1.  Run the following command in the `src-tauri` folder to add the plugin to the project's dependencies in `Cargo.toml`:
 46 | 
 47 |             ```sh frame=none
 48 |             cargo add tauri-plugin-biometric --target 'cfg(any(target_os = "android", target_os = "ios"))'
 49 |             ```
 50 | 
 51 |         2.  Modify `lib.rs` to initialize the plugin:
 52 | 
