 51 |             ```
 52 | 
 53 |     		2.	Modify `lib.rs` to initialize the plugin:
 54 | 
 55 |             ```rust title="src-tauri/src/lib.rs" ins={5-6}
 56 |             #[cfg_attr(mobile, tauri::mobile_entry_point)]
 57 |             pub fn run() {
