 53 | 
 54 |       2.  Modify `lib.rs` to initialize the plugin:
 55 | 
 56 |           ```rust title="src-tauri/src/lib.rs" ins={5-6}
 57 |           #[cfg_attr(mobile, tauri::mobile_entry_point)]
 58 |           pub fn run() {
