173 | - `myapp.AppImage.tar.gz` - The updater bundle.
174 | - `myapp.AppImage.tar.gz.sig` - The signature of the update bundle.
175 | 
176 | On macOS, Tauri will create a .tar.gz archive from the application bundle inside the target/release/bundle/macos/ folder:
177 | 
