179 | - `myapp.app.tar.gz` - The updater bundle.
180 | - `myapp.app.tar.gz.sig` - The signature of the update bundle.
181 | 
182 | On Windows, Tauri will create .zip archives from the MSI and NSIS installers inside the target/release/bundle/msi/ and target/release/bundle/nsis folders:
183 | 
184 | - `myapp-setup.exe` - The standard app bundle.
